      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOUTIQUE BELLE (9) missed narrowly two back and again last time out when beaten 1.6L at Pinjarra last time out. Out to the mile now for the first time looks to suit and she can pick up her maiden win now. SHOW ON THE ROAD (5) is knocking on the door of a maiden win, crossing from out wide to sit handy and just miss by 0.4L at Pinjarra last time. That form has worked out well and he maps perfectly off the inside draw. Gets Brad Parnham on board now and he looks the main danger. AGENT REMINGTON (3) looks a nice horse on the rise and steps out in trip today which looks to suit. Should land in a handy position and he makes plenty of appeal with his upside. BONDI BUSINESS (2) is third-up now and can be in the finish. PRETEY ROYAL (7) has to be included on her recent form.",
